title: Ebro In The Morning - Ebro Is Back + The Gang's All Here
itunes:author: Ebro In The Morning on HOT 97
itunes:summary:
Ebro, Rosenberg and Laura Stylez star in HOT97's flagship program Ebro in the Morning - this episode aired on 1/10/2022.

Ebro, Rosenberg, Laura Stylez, and the crew are back in the studio - New York is cold, but Ebro back is on the show ! Catch up with your favorite team in media! Find out who played themselves and how the Gurus can help!
